# Digmar UI tokens (`src/styles/global.css`)

Shared `@layer components` utilities:

- **`.layout-container`** — max width + horizontal padding
- **`.layout-section`** — vertical section spacing
- **`.card-surface`** — white card, border, light shadow
- **`.text-eyebrow`** — small uppercase accent
- **`.btn`**, **`.btn-primary`**, **`.btn-secondary`** — solid emerald primary; neutral secondary

Prefer these over one-off duplicate class strings for consistency. Marketing pages: light backgrounds (`bg-slate-50`, white cards), minimal gradients.
